$Id: TODO,v 1.8 2002-09-26 20:50:01 mschimek Exp $

* 001 io: Add io-dvb. Generally speaking the i/o api is poor,
  should be improved.
* 002 decoder.c: Having a public vbi_decoder and vbi_bit_slicer is bad.
  Should be both opaque (except slicer in vbi_decoder),
  with new public vbi_sampling_parameters structure.
* 003 search.c: Add vbi_wst_level.
* 004 exp-gfx.c: draw_*_page_region different formats, custom fonts.
* 005 packet.c: Add filter for data pages (EPG etc).
* 006 Finish vbi_fetch_* reference counting.
* 007 Improve TTX page cache.
* 008 TTX export: Make blockgfx replacement smarter.
* 009 Streaming subtitles (as opposed to exporting single pages).
* 010 SGML error reporting. (Not sure anymore if this is
  really worth the trouble.)
* 011 Think about ttx header samples (p100) for stations not transmitting
  a CNI (instead of guessing the name from ttx). May use VTX to create
  samples.
* 012 Program info from TTX (8/30 and VPS/PDC).
* 013 Can we replace ASCII/Latin-1/local by a single char set? Perhaps UTF-8?
* 014 Suppose Turkish currency sign U+E800 can be replaced by U+20A4,
  Unicode 3.1: "20A4 LIRA SIGN\n* Italy, Turkey"
* 015 Improve TTX roll header + serial (Mxx increment).
* 016 Add VPT decoder.
* 017 Make Teletext column 41 optional.
* 018 http://telepresence.dmem.strath.ac.uk/bt848/
* 019 print should translate linefeeds to target charset (wchar...)
* 020 VR triggers from VPS/PDC/XDS.
* 021 Not relocatable (bindtextdomain)

